10
00:00:36,433 --> 00:00:40,064
Dekho kitna beautiful pattern banta hai! Sphere

11
00:00:40,164 --> 00:00:43,557
ka relative motion cycloid curve banata hai.

12
00:00:43,666 --> 00:00:49,184
Is complex motion mein energy conservation, angular momentum, rolling

13
00:00:49,284 --> 00:00:54,150
